sarplot - a script to turn the extremly useful data produced from sar/sysstat into ASCII graphs using gnuplot

Example plot of 1 minute load averages:

$ ./sarplot load

 0.05 ++-+---+--+---+--+--+---+--+---+--+--+---+--+---+--+--+---+--+*--+-++
